prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D botanical illustration for a greeting card. A humorous and vibrant scene celebrating a birthday, featuring cartoon versions of Jordan and Lao Lao from the reference photo. Jordan, wearing a solid dark blue t-shirt, is playfully snowboarding down a giant, perfectly marbled slice of wagyu steak that curves like a snowy hill. He has a wide, joyful expression. Lao Lao, wearing her white zip-up jacket and glasses, is laughing as she sits at the bottom of the "wagyu hill" at a small table, holding chopsticks and gleefully plucking sushi rolls off a conveyor belt that weaves around the scene. The conveyor belt also carries illustrated Chinese takeout boxes and lines of glowing green computer code that flow like a river. The entire scene is framed by a lush botanical border of wasabi-green leaves, delicate ginger-flower blossoms, and bamboo stalks, all on a clean, light background.

Centered in a clear space is the text "Happy Birthday, Jordan" in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script.
